Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = LG(U1)
Type    = Artifact Creature (3/3)
Cost    = 5
Artist  = Melissa Benson

Text(LG): All walls able to block Marble Priest must do so. Walls able to
          block more  than one creature can still do so. If blocking wall
          is compelled to block more creatures than it is legally able to,
          defender chooses which of these attacking creatures to block, but
          must block as many creatures as it legally can. Damage dealt to
          Marble Priest from walls during combat is reduced to 0.

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

