@{b}Triassic Egg@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = LG(R) / CR(U1)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Dan Frazier

Text(CR): <3T>: Put a hatchling counter on Triassic Egg.
          <0>: Sacrifice Triassic Egg to take target creature from your
